      <h1>Information</h1>
      <p>Niklay Wiborny, for tstfie. Creating conceptual sneaker collections and music projects. The work approaches design as a way of thinking in public, using digital mock-ups not as blueprints for manufacturing, but as conceptual, narrative-conveying art projects built around curated themes.<br><br>Emerging publicly in 2024, the first cycle moved through twelve sneaker collections exploring ambition, devotion, and self-construction. SAINT PABLO, the 23/24 cycleâ€™s conclusion, set a vocabulary of maximalist detail, extreme devotion, and self-absorbed conviction. Its follow-up, T.W.I.Y WAVES, pulled back, choosing simplicity. The following collections disrupted both paths, further dissolving certainty and stability in the process, culminating in Periapsis (2025). The 34-design collection navigates depersonalisation, orbit, and distance, working through guilt and the oscillation between self-erasure and discovery, a response to a previous creative period.<br><br>In parallel: music. Early demos and mixtapes such as Interludes (2024) established a foundational sound. INTERLUDIUMAR (2024) gathered the archetypal motifs in a 10-track instrumental debut, inviting multiple collaborative singles in the following months. Collaborations rolling out eventually lead to the 10-minute posse cut Der Freestyle, der Brennt (2024) releasing on the same day as the LCKSPTXIYGNUWITXD sneaker collection. The output-heavy year of 2024 resolved with the 10-track mixtape SAINTIFICATION in December and a further victory lap in the compilation mixtape What&#x27;s That, Poetry?<br><br>Silence shaped the following year: a bi-monthly, low-promo release schedule structured the creative output of 2025. Circle of Fifths presented a rare image: twelve slowly unfolding instrumentals built around repetition culminated into the April release. SPIRITS followed in August, leaning into theater, faith, and chaos. The EP showed a work of collapse, later revisited in a Legacy release.<br><br>Across mediums, tstfie exudes unapologetic presence, abandoning stability. Consistency almost exclusively retains through fundamental tensions: the pull between ambition and surrender, shame and silence and ascent and return creates a secular vessel to convey sacred ideas. The work documents the difficulty of self-depiction in an ongoing oscillation between clarity and impulsiveness.</p>
